Package: spca
Type: Package
Title: Sparse Principal Component Analysis
Version: 0.6
Date: 2014-10-24
Author: Giovanni Maria Merola
Maintainer: Giovanni Merola <lsspca@gmail.com>
Description: Computes Least Squares Sparse Principal Components either by a
    Branch-and-Bound search or with an iterative Backward Elimination
    algorithm. There functions for exploring different solutions, so to
    determine the best cardinalities and for plotting and printing the results
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    formatR,
    knitr,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2
Imports:
    MASS
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
